{"lastModified":1754992450788,"uri":"c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nIf you are a sailing enthusiast and want to spend an unforgettable holiday on the Island of Elba, there is no better way to do it than on board our splendid Bavaria C42 Supereva, a luxury monohull sailing boat. With 3 spacious cabins and two bathrooms, she offers extraordinary performance, this vessel will offer you a one-of-a-kind sailing experience.\n\nTechnical characteristics of the Bavaria C42 Supereva\nThe Bavaria C42 Supereva stands out for its elegant and modern design. Extremely Spacious and Bright. The interiors are designed down to the smallest details, with large windows that allow a breathtaking panoramic view of the ocean. The bow cabin, equipped with a very spacious double bed and private bathroom, offers unparalleled comfort.\n\nThe 3 cabins are large and well lit.\nOn board the C42 Supereva, you will find 3 very spacious cabins that offer enough space to relax and enjoy sailing in 3 couples with all the comfort they deserve.\n\nExceptional Performance:\nthe Bavaria C42 Supereva has a fully battened mainsail and offers exceptional performance at sea. She is an easy sailboat to handle. With a size that is not too high it allows any maneuver. She offers smooth and safe navigation even for the less experienced.\n\nSpacious Salon: The U-shaped seating area on the starboard side and the lounge bench on the port side can easily accommodate up to eight people for a cozy dinner in port. As in classic layouts, the L-shaped pantry is located on the port side. The kitchen is fully equipped.\n\nWhat better way to experience a fantastic sailing holiday on the Island of Elba with the rental of the Bavaria C42 Supereva, fresh from the shipyard, in its first charter season.\n\nSail the crystal clear waters and discover the hidden bays of the Island of Elba with Marina Yacht Charter. You can sail along the coast and discover secluded coves, visit picturesque fishing villages and savor delicious local cuisine.\n\nBook Now, Fill out the Information Request form. Sails every Saturday from San Vincenzo, LI\n\nOur Bavaria C42 Supereva YEAR 2023 represents the perfect mix of high-level performance and luxurious comfort. Sailing on the Island of Elba aboard this magnificent vessel will give you unforgettable moments and an unparalleled sailing experience. Don't wait any longer, book your bareboat rental now and get ready to experience a dream holiday!\n\nDon't forget to post your memories on our social media.","blueprint":{"name":"SUPEREVA","images":["/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::e1bae060-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::efb0f150-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::f1c7c360-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::f66678d0-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::f666c6f0-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::f6654050-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::fce252b0-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::fce14140-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9699759712::vessel::f9aa8ca0-b6af-11ee-92d6-41e709e6ce42::assets::fce2c7e0-b6e9-11ee-ba57-7dd82052e495.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/me